<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="function-points">Function points<a href="https://fanghaoming.github.io/blog/%E5%81%9A%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AAvscode%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6#function-points" class="hash-link" aria-label="Function points的直接链接" title="Function points的直接链接">​</a></h2>
